data.description: Spacious one-level Ranch home in Universal City, with easy access to the big city conveniences of San Antonio, or the relaxation of Texas Hill Country parks and waterways. Beautiful, original parquet floors and a wood-burning fireplace create a cozy family room, open to the kitchen. Recently updated kitchen and bath with granite countertops. With several living spaces and a formal dining room, the versatility of the home is perfect for any lifestyle. A cozy, large den with a half-bath, built-in shelving and sliding doors to the screened porch offers a third living space or large office. The huge backyard has privacy fencing and behind that a noise barrier wall separating it from the access road behind the property.
